      "be844055623_html": "Premium Collection",
      "be882200306_html": "The Heritage",
      "be207850461821_html": "Shop by Favorites<br>",
      "be129433467666_html": "Discover Our Story&nbsp;<div>A Journey of Passion &amp; Care</div>",
      "be1466251462_html": "Made in UK",
      "be953180037_html": "Proudly produced in a high-standard UK facility, following strict safety and quality regulations to ensure every meal is nutritious, safe, and beneficial for your pet’s well-being.",
      "be1387199535_html": "Learn more",
      "be380390507_html": "Made by Experts",
      "be209359430_html": "Carefully formulated by a team of renowned veterinary specialists and pet nutritionists, ensuring a balanced and scientifically backed diet for optimal pet health.",
      "be922502881_html": "Trusted by Pet",
      "be1630923996_html": "Recommended by millions of pet parents and veterinarians worldwide for its premium quality, natural ingredients, and proven health benefits.",
      "be1222705409_html": "100% Organic",
      "be1368020096_html": "Crafted with premium, all-natural ingredients, free from gluten, artificial preservatives, or synthetic flavors, offering a wholesome and easily digestible meal for pets of all ages.",
      "be170435297460_html": "Leading the Future of&nbsp;<div>Dry Pet Food in the UK</div>",
      "be1370898622_html": "We are dedicated to providing high-quality, nutritious meals for pets of all ages. From carefully crafted dry food to delicious treats, our products are trusted by pet owners and recommended by experts. As one of the fastest-growing brands in the UK, we continue to set new standards in pet nutrition.",
      "be1688768986_html": "Expertly Formulated&nbsp;",
      "be2059188399_html": "Developed with leading veterinarians for optimal pet health.",
      "be243761511_html": "Highest Quality Standards",
      "be456613558_html": "Produced in state-of-the-art UK facilities with rigorous safety checks.",
      "be1388892178_html": "Natural &amp; Nutritious",
      "be1502752523_html": "Made from 100% organic ingredients, free from artificial additives.",
      "be1671691340_html": "Loved by Pets &amp; Owners",
      "be644398318_html": "A top choice for thousands of pet parents across the UK.",
      "be282195252_html": "Shop now",
      "be121137253935_html": "Our Best Selling<div>Products</div>",
      "be649020154_html": "Add to cart",
      "be1538394658_html": "Sold out",
      "be719299147_html": "Choose options",
      "be65290051_html": "Color",
      "be978022322_html": "From {{ price_min }}",
      "be1950827197_html": "{{ price_normal }}",
      "be679965416_html": "Quick view",
      "be849688199_html": "Save {sale}%",
      "be1582798470117_html": "This store is a demo of the Beae template. The products from this store are from the catalog of <b>Wagg Pet Foods</b>",
      "be724049415_html": "Evething for your dogs",
      "be1559034619_html": "Accessories and food for your loving dogs",
      "be2109892357_html": "Get more offer",
      "be1302842817_html": "Frequently Ask Questions",
      "be224494812_html": "Get All Your questions Answered Here",
      "be2039440006_html": "Have questions? here are quick answers to some of the most common queries about my services and process",
      "be1617769172_html": "Ask A Question",
      "be1130591367_html": "What ingredients do you use in your pet food?",
      "be359767110_html": "Is your pet food suitable for all breeds and ages?",
      "be1145721223_html": "How long does shipping take?",
      "be682008240_html": "What is your return policy?",
      "be831271963_html": "Do you offer subscriptions for pet food?",
      "be821814385_html": "How do I know which food is best for my pet?",
      "be2004368555_html": "Our pet food is made with high-quality, natural ingredients, including fresh meat, vegetables, and essential nutrients. We avoid artificial preservatives and fillers to ensure your pet’s health.",
      "be695263533_html": "Yes! Our pet food is formulated to be nutritionally balanced for all breeds and life stages, from playful puppies and kittens to senior pets. If your pet has specific dietary needs, we recommend consulting your veterinarian.",
      "be2061213514201_html": "We process orders within 1-2 business days. Standard shipping takes<b> 3-5 business days</b>, while expedited shipping options are available at checkout. Delivery times may vary based on your location.",
      "be1177821808_html": "We offer a 100% satisfaction guarantee! If you're not happy with your purchase, you can return it within 30 days for a full refund. Please note that opened food packages may not be eligible for return due to safety reasons. Contact our support team for assistance.",
      "be2022680724_html": "Yes! We offer flexible subscription plans so your pet never runs out of fresh food. You can customize your delivery schedule and modify or cancel anytime. Plus, subscribers get exclusive discounts!",
      "be867322082_html": "We provide a detailed feeding guide based on your pet’s age, weight, and dietary needs. If you need personalized recommendations, our team is happy to assist, or you can consult your veterinarian for expert advice.",
      "be297602444_html": "Instagram Feed",
      "be1276713260_html": "Discover our customers' lovely moments!",
      "be1585610763_html": "Special Offer",
      "be273672242852_html": "<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span color=\"#ffffff\" style=\"color:var(--beae-global-colors-white);--bts-mobile-font-size:35px;--bts-mobile-line-height:45px;--bts-mobile-letter-spacing:normal;--bts-font-size:54px;--bts-line-height:70px;--bts-letter-spacing:normal;\" class=\"beae-text-size\">Get </span><span style=\"--bts-mobile-font-size:35px;--bts-mobile-line-height:45px;--bts-mobile-letter-spacing:normal;--bts-font-size:54px;--bts-line-height:70px;--bts-letter-spacing:normal;color:var(--beae-global-colors-secondary_600);\" class=\"beae-text-size\">20%</span><span color=\"#ffffff\" style=\"color:var(--beae-global-colors-white);--bts-mobile-font-size:35px;--bts-mobile-line-height:45px;--bts-mobile-letter-spacing:normal;--bts-font-size:54px;--bts-line-height:70px;--bts-letter-spacing:normal;\" class=\"beae-text-size\"> Off Your Order Today!</span></span>"
    },
    "beae-wp-1": {
      "be76480_html": "N/A",
      "be2093686401_html": "CAnon Wp-1, A robust, waterproof point &amp; shoot",
      "be1148619676396_html": "The WP-1 is a fun and capable water resistant and shockproof camera ready for your next adventure whether thats on land or sea. It features a sharp 32mm f/3.5 lens, a fast and smart autofocus, built-in flash, and a macro mode with a minimum focus distance of just 45cm! This rugged but compact and light-weight camera is the perfect companion for your next vacation.<div><br></div><div><br></div>",
      "be1701336254580_html": "The Canon WP-1 aka the Canon Sure Shot A1 aka the Canon Prima AS 1 and sometimes even occasionally known as the naughty Auto Boy D5 is a (debatebly) waterproof camera from the early 90s. It’s wacky looking, sturdy but surprisingly competent as the camera to keep in your pocket.&nbsp;<div><br></div><div>The camera comes in a couple of versions, you can tell which is which because the name is on the front. The insides are nearly identical, though some of the A1’s were reportedly using a different type of plastic that seems to yellow really badly with age.</div><div><br></div>",
      "be850461540_html": "Sharp &amp; cinematic",
      "be1270732317389_html": "<!-- x-tinymce/html -->The WP-1 is a fun and capable water resistant and shockproof camera ready for your next adventure whether thats on land or sea. It features a sharp 32mm f/3.5 lens, a fast and smart autofocus, built-in flash, and a macro mode with a minimum focus distance of just 45cm! This rugged but compact and light-weight camera is the perfect companion for your next vacation.",
      "be2582855_html": "Sony",
      "be267682879_html": "Sony is one of the largest electronics manufacturers in the world. They make everything from cameras and TVs to a broad line of headphones suited to diverse needs. Whether you're looking for noise cancelling over-ears to help cut down ambient sound during your commute, sports-oriented earbuds with great stability, or niche products like bassy headphones, Sony can meet your needs. Many Sony headphones are also compatible with the Sony | Headphones Connect app, which offers customization features like an EQ or button mapping. However, sorting through their large selection can be overwhelming, especially as there's a lot of overlap between models. Still, their high-end Bluetooth models are among the best we've tested, offering versatile performance for most users.",
      "be181593208_html": "The Sony WH-1000XM4 Wireless are a solid choice if you prefer an over-ear fit. Although they're the previous generation of the Sony WH-1000XM5 Wireless, they offer a better overall noise isolation performance, thanks to their powerful ANC. They're also comfortable enough for long listening sessions and last over 37 hours continuously. With their companion app's graphic EQ and presets, you can tweak their bass-heavy sound to suit your tastes. If you prefer an in-ear fit, the best Sony earbuds we've tested are the Sony WF-1000XM5 Truly Wireless. These noise cancelling Bluetooth in-ears are a great choice for on-the-go use, though they aren't quite as comfortable or as well-built as the over-ear alternative, and their battery life isn't as long-lasting.",
      "be63476538_html": "Apple",
      "be1379335536_html": "The Apple AirPods Pro (2nd generation) Truly Wireless are the best Apple headphones we've tested. These in-ears follow the Apple AirPods Pro Truly Wireless and have an even better ANC system than the original. They can easily cut out noise from passing traffic and noisy coworkers. Their default sound profile is warm, with more bass than the original Pro and a balanced mix that's versatile enough for most genres of music. While their nearly six-hour continuous battery life is short, their carrying case holds four additional charges, and the buds go into standby mode when not in use. If you prefer over-ear headphones, you may want to consider the Apple AirPods Max Wireless, which are premium noise cancelling headphones with a sleek aluminum design. However, they're heavy and can be fatiguing for long listening sessions.",
      "be944311290_html": "Sennheiser",
      "be1129217801_html": "Sennheiser was originally established in Germany, and now, with international hubs, their products are well-reputed among musicians and audiophiles. They're renowned for their live music and music production equipment, like microphones and peripherals, but they also make a small selection of soundbars. The manufacturer's wide range of open-back headphones with good performance at various price points contributes to their prestige. However, they also make Bluetooth models for more casual listening and dedicated TV headphones to enjoy your favorite shows wirelessly without sync issues. They make over- and in-ears but don't have many truly wireless models, although the ones they have tend to perform well. Also, like Sony, it can be hard to know which of their headphones provide the best value since they have so many overlapping models with only minor differences. They're a reliable brand with a good reputation for consistent products worth recommendation.",
      "be1254330172_html": "The best Sennheiser headphones we've tested are the Sennheiser HD 800 S. These reference-class over-ears have an open-back design, resulting in a spacious and immersive soundstage. Combined with an expertly tuned sound signature, they're a stellar choice for listening to your favorite high-fidelity tracks in a quiet room. They're quite the investment, so audiophiles on a budget will want to consider the more affordable Sennheiser HD 560S, which don't sound as immersive but provide better value for the price. If you prefer the versatility of a wireless noise cancelling design, the Sennheiser MOMENTUM 4 Wireless have a bass-rich sound with a stylish, comfortable fit for everyday use. However, they offer a less immersive listening experience due to their closed-back design.",
      "be73236_html": "JBL",
      "be1986541544_html": "JBL is an American manufacturer that offers various audio equipment like speakers and headphones. A subsidiary of Harman, most of their extensive lineup of headphones feature a neutral default sound profile, which will please most listeners. However, select models have excited bass- and treble-heavy, V-shaped frequency responses. Some of these headphones are compatible with the JBL Headphones app, offering a parametric EQ and presets to customize them. Particularly, JBL is one of the few brands with a wide selection of on-ear headphones, which seem to be a less common style these days. JBL also produces a variety of headphones at different price points, and many of them come in a couple of fun colorways, so there's something for everyone from this brand.",
      "be605291640_html": "The JBL Live Pro 2 TWS True Wireless are the best JBL headphones we've tested. These well-built buds offer versatile performance and have a few handy features for day-to-day life. They have an ANC feature with a great overall performance, blocking everything from bus and plane engines to office chatter. With their ANC on, they also last over eight hours continuously, and their case holds an extra three charges if you need it. Their V-shaped sound is well-suited for genres like rock and pop, but if you prefer a different sound, their companion app has a parametric EQ and presets so you can fine-tune their sound. They can also be paired with up to two devices at a time, which is handy if you like to switch audio sources.",
      "be1819699109_html": "Share:",
      "be762197622_html": "Link copied",
